---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <style is:global>
      :root {
        --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        --color-bg: #ffffff;
        --color-text: #222;
        --color-accent: #10b981;
        --max-width: 1400px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <h1>Ben van Glabbeek</h1>
      <p>"If you want to build a ship, don't drum up the people... vast and endless sea." - Antoine de Saint-Exupéry</p>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/appalachian-trail">Appalachian Trail</a>
        <a href="/transcen-digital">Transcen.Digital</a>
